From: 
To: 
Subject: RE: Subpoena Log and Subpoena Records 
Date: Thu. 31 Oct 2019 15:54:07 +0000 
You have co-owner status now. Congratulations! 
From
Sent: 
To: 
Subject: RE: Subpoena Log and Subpoena Records 
Can you either change my folder settings from editor to co-owner so that I can add her? Or just add her directly? 
Whatever is easiest. I will go ahead and re-upload all the subpoenas and returns since there appear to be no files in the 
folder for either. 
From: 
Sent: Thursday, October 31, 2019 1:47 AM 
To: 
Subject: RE: Subpoena Log and Subpoena Records 
Yes, I think she needs two things: 
1. Access to USAFX. I just added you to the folder. 
2. All the subpoena returns re-loaded since they've expired since I last uploaded them. 
From: 
Sent: Tuesday, October 29, 2019 5:23 PM 
To: 
Subject: FW: Subpoena Log and Subpoena Records 
Is there a  folder/is what she is talking about on there? 
From: 
Sent: Tuesday, October 29, 2019 3:04 PM 
To: 
Subject: FW: Subpoena Log and Subpoena Records 
Hi 
I was just going through all of my emails for the Epstein investigation to make sure everything was in the case file —
realized that I never asked to get access to USAFX in order to see all the subpoenas and returns.... Can you give me access 
and is everything still posted on that site? 
Thanks 
so much — 
Special Agent 
Fill New York Field Office 
EFTA00031401

Violent Crimes Task Force 
From: 
Sent: Saturday, August 17, 2019 4:27 PM 
To: 
Cc: 
Subject: Subpoena Log and Subpoena Records 
Hi, 
Attached is a log of all the subpoenas we've served and what has come back. I've posted the actual subpoenas and 
returns on the USAO's FTP site, called USAFX. Carpenter and Gildea already have access to USAFX. For everyone else, 
you'll need an account which is very easy. Will can help you get an account — I think he'll just need your cellphone 
number. 
Let us know if you have any questions. 
• 
Assistant United States Attorney 
United States Attorney's Office 
Southern District of New York 
One St. Andrew's Plaza 
New York. New York 10007 
EFTA00031402
